Package: biocclasses
Title: The Bioconductor Classes Handbook
Description: The S4 system is preferred for its strict
  structure, robust error checking, and advanced dispatch capabilities, which
  are essential for complex collaborative projects. Bioconductor leverages this
  system to ensure interoperability and reliable code reuse across hundreds of
  biological data analysis packages. The handbook provides an extensive catalog
  of existing core S4 classes and encourages developers to reuse these
  established foundations rather than creating redundant new ones.
